 ~/ t.punchRES
 ~/ macro to punch out Residential Land Use
 ~/ usage: emme2 clear 314 batch -m "t.punchRES"
 ~/ DML 2.14.92
 1        /list a matrix
 3           /several
 mo19     /single family detached houses
 mo20     /single family attached town houses
 mo21     /garden apartments
 mo22     /high rise apartments
  
  
 n        /no submatrix
 q
 q
